{"tid":2411171,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(coinmaster)騙案，求起底*警惕文*","createTime":"2021-02-17T06:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T16:52:47.000Z","uid":68990,"like":3,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"942e67a79e374fd85917c95b2cc80f3809028d28","tid":2411171,"uid":68990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:55:42.000Z","msg":"近來，身邊唔少好友都有玩宜隻Game，因為台灣廣告打得火熱，紅到埋黎香港，大家都會記得「珍妮佛羅培茲」<br />\n亦唔少人會選擇課金，當中可能透過Ig Shop或者 Carousell去搵平既代課金...<br />\n亦有騙徒去利用未成熟既少年貪平既心態落手...<br />\n<br />\n以下方享其中既騙案；<br />\n相信宜間Ig Shop都呃左唔少人既錢，希望透過連登咁多位Ching幫手起底，為佢地討回被呃既錢，同埋警惕大家。<br />\n<br />\n👇🏼黑店👇🏼 幫手Report<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MiqZyb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MiqZyb.png&h=175878a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n👇🏼案例👇🏼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hpOVCsn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhpOVCsn.jpg&h=fbf0979f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sK3qZFL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsK3qZFL.jpg&h=b863de27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHgsty9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHgsty9.jpg&h=4659d8fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RLvT8zd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRLvT8zd.jpg&h=fdf43ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥<br />\n該店店主等D人入完數，佢自己收到錢，通常就會拎返張舊圖出黎同人地講無貨。<br />\n然後一直拖延 唔肯退錢，IG Profile標榜不成功可以退錢，原來大隻廣 得個講字！<br />\n👇🏼騙徒支那寶QR CODE👇🏼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocWgmUo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocWgmUo.png&h=6548385f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqDVCsM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqDVCsM.png&h=da4c7f7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n👇🏼FPS ID👇🏼<br />\n<img src=\"https: